title: 11/03: Week 9 Recap - Backfield Shake-ups (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
Do we have new lead RBs in BUF, KC and TB? We'll discuss those situations, but first let's get to the Best of Week 9 (3:00) as Russell Wilson and Tyler Lockett were phenomenal and Zach Ertz might be back! Oh, and what the heck happened to the Packers today (13:00)? ... A look at the big news (15:42) and an early look at the Waiver Wire (17:25). How much are we liking Zach Pascal? Ronald Jones? Then Dave and Heath give their Winners (21:56) like D.J. Moore and Devin Singletary and Losers (30:45) like Juju Smith-Schuster and Le'Veon Bell. We'll also get the Worryometer out (36:54) for struggling WRs like Allen Robinson and Terry McLaurin ... A recap of each game with a "Believe it or Not" from Heath (45:15). Is Melvin Gordon a stud again? Is Matthew Stafford legit? What about Kirk Cousins? ... Email us at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
